    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/2fa7afedeedc1988c77d15d0656856d2.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>她是黑暗魔法师，伟大克拉肯尼亚拉托的使徒。<br>从这一刻起，她开始猎取活生生的祭品献给尼亚拉托<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让我们猎杀人类，收集他们的衣物。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/cf480bebf551c3a5eccb1c47ea0588a4.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>克拉肯喜欢穿着漂亮衣服的人类。<br>收集各种服装来取悦伟大的克拉肯。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单而极度刺激的动作体验。 </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/1e090855c82acb570799f89d4cebf458.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏的操作和系统非常简单易用，<br>爽快的动作让你沉浸在猎杀愚蠢人类的快感中。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >给那些渺小的人类来一场身体上的教育。 </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/b8f90a2434feb03a69e9589b09771900.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>对愚蠢的人类使用克拉肯是一种奢侈。<br>教育从摔跤开始。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用克拉肯的力量束缚活生生的祭品。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.poster.avif?t=1750972346\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.webm?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303320/extras/bb8ef01d5472176b5e90195a16622d77.mp4?t=1750972346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在合适的时机召唤克拉肯来束缚人类。你可以从捕获的活生生的祭品中获得许多宝贵的奖励。",
